                        <p>Sincerely,</p>
<p><a href="https://www.change.org/p/president-richard-brodhead-invigorate-duke-university-s-commitment-to-an-open-intellectual-climate-on-campus?recruiter=470281330&utm_source=share_for_starters&utm_medium=copyLink" target="_blank">The Duke Open Campus Coalition</a></p>
<p><em>Signed:&nbsp;Tyler Fredricks ‘16,&nbsp;Pi Praveen ‘16,&nbsp;Breanna Atkinson ‘16,&nbsp;Ian Chang ‘19,&nbsp;Zach Heater ‘17,&nbsp;Brian Hopkins ‘16,&nbsp;Brendan McCartney ‘16,&nbsp;Gerardo Parraga ‘18,&nbsp;Sabriyya Pate ‘19,&nbsp;Lopa Rahman ‘16,&nbsp;Victoria Treboschi ‘15, and&nbsp;</em><em>Caroline Wang ‘19.</em></p>

